"""Tests optimization as a single call."""
_, _, _, model = optimize(parameters=[{'name': 'x1', 'type': 'range',
    'bounds': [-10.0, 10.0]}, {'name': 'x2', 'type': 'range', 'bounds': [-
    10.0, 10.0]}], evaluation_function=lambda p: (p['x1'] + 2 * p['x2'] - 7
    ) ** 2 + (2 * p['x1'] + p['x2'] - 5) ** 2, minimize=True, total_trials=
    5, random_seed=12345)
self.assertEqual(12345, model.model.seed)
